.gov.uk/education/medieval/magna-carta/","urlTitle":"National Archives - Magna Carta","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705188,"age":74,"year":"1224","julianDay":2168117,"title":"France Declares War on England","description":"France declared war on England as Louis VIII of France attacked Poitou and northern Gascony.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes Fitz-Ranulf was born in 1150, in Chaffcombe, Somerset, England as the daughter of Robert Fitz-Ranulf. She married John de Aure in 1190, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. She died in 1250, in her hometown, at the age of 100."},"et":{"1150–1250":"1150–1250","1144–Male":"1144–Surnud","1192–Male":"1192–Surnud","1195–Female":"1195–Surnud","1200–Female":"1200–Surnud","1204–1285":"1204–1285","1130–Male":"1130–Surnud","1190":"1190","before 1200":"enne 1200","1198":"1198","1285":"1285","1130":"1130","1195":"1195","1250":"1250","1150":"1150","1192":"1192","1204":"1204","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","1200":"1200","1144":"1144","England":"England","France":"Prantsusmaa","Chaffcombe, Somerset, England":"Chaffcombe, Somerset, England"},"fi":{"1150–1250":"1150–1250","1144–Male":"1144–Kuollut","1192–Male":"1192–Kuollut","1195–Female":"1195–Kuollut","1200–Female":"1200–Kuollut","1204–1285":"1204–1285","1130–Male":"1130–Kuollut","1190":"1190","before 1200":"ennen vuotta 1200","1198":"1198","1285":"1285","1130":"1130","1195":"1195","1250":"1250","1150":"1150","1192":"1192","1204":"1204","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","1200":"1200","1144":"1144","England":"England","France":"Ranska","Chaffcombe, Somerset, England":"Chaffcombe, Somerset, England"},"fr":{"1150–1250":"1150–1250","1144–Male":"1144–Décédé","1192–Male":"1192–Décédé","1195–Female":"1195–Décédée","1200–Female":"1200–Décédée","1204–1285":"1204–1285","1130–Male":"1130–Décédé","1190":"1190","before 1200":"avant 1200","1198":"1198","1285":"1285","1130":"1130","1195":"1195","1250":"1250","1150":"1150","1192":"1192","1204":"1204","1215":"1215","1224"